question: Oaⁿ-tiâⁿ ê 'Current ratio' sī sím-mih hō͘ só͘-ū bōe chhāi-lâi ê kong-si ('Survive?' = 0)?
Koe-siong ê sán-gia̍p, teh kiû kiù-sán ê, kap ''Siâⁿ-chiàⁿ tùi kó͘-tēng sán-gia̍p ê pí-lu̍t'' siâⁿ--khì 200 ê siông ê, chhiáⁿ lia̍t chhut lâi.
In the surviving company ('Survive?' = 1), which one get the highest 'Quick ratio', meaning the best liquidity position?
Koh-iáⁿ ê chio̍h-gia̍p tùi chha-sòe ê siau-bē-chiá ê lē-tîm hō͘ kò͘-tēng chu-sán ê tit-siat pí sí ê kong-si khah-chē nn̄g-pái, leh-iáⁿ ê lâi-thâu ê kang-gia̍p sī sím-mih?

Tī só͘-ū siūⁿ-oa̍h ê kong-si ê chóng 'Tiⁿ-bâi pí' (Current ratio) tang-tiong, 'Bāng-thih sán-phín chè-chok' (Steel products manufacture) chit keng kong-si chiem kah chek-sú percentage? Chhiáⁿ-chhiáⁿ tōa-sò͘ siâⁿ chi̍t ūi.
Keng-tōa ê su-bī hō͘ 'Pianos chè-chō chhe-bē' kong-si ê 'Tī-sî sū-lē' chha-put-to 50 hūn, ài chāi chāi hō͘ hō͘-chú ê kong-si ê sái ê 'Tī-sî sū-lē' ê tiong-kan-sò͘ ūi-hô?
Tùi chit ê chu-liā lâi kóng, koh-khah cao ê 'Quick ratio' ū siūⁿ chē-chē ê sîng-kong cheng-kái bô? Chhái-iōng chu-liā lâi kái-soeh lí ê koan-tiám.
answer: Bōe, koh-khah cao ê 'Quick ratio' bōe chōe kà sîng-kong ê cheng-kái. Tī saⁿ ê tùi-chhōe ê sán-gia̍p (Koh-chiáⁿ tōe chòe kóng kah 'Phonographs'), chi̍t ê siūⁿ ê ūi bat ū koh-khah cao ê phiau-chún, m̄-koh 'Meat-packing' sán-gia̍p chē kā chi̍t ê tò-liân-chhiú chha-m̄-po͘. Hit ê siūⁿ ê 'Meat-packing' kong-si bat ū chi̍t ê 'Quick ratio' 302, che sī koh-khah cao koh-khah chē ê 221 phiau-chún ê i ê siūⁿ ê tùi-chhiat.

question: Gán-chiàu 'Current ratio' lâi koân-sîn, siáⁿ chi̍t keng kong-si sī hui-siông ê tū-chha̍t, chiàⁿ-báⁿ i ê siau-uánn kiat-kó sī siáⁿ-mih?
answer: Chha̍h-chè kah chhiam-á chè-chō sán-ye̍h ê kong-si sī tū-chha̍t, i ê 'Current ratio' sī 2525. Chit keng kong-si bōe siau-uánn (Survive? = 0).

question: Koh-khoán kong-gia̍p sī ū kāng-khóan ê chio̍h-oa̍h kah bô-chia̍h-oa̍h ê kong-si tī chit ê chhit-sò͘-lūi lāi-bīn?
answer: Cotton textile industry of New England

question: Nāi-kū sī tūi 'sán-phín hāu-lī' chòe 'bōe-chhut-lâi ê sán-phín chi̍t-ê sán-phín' lâi tōaⁿ-sǹg, nn̄g ê sí-khì ê kong-si (Pair ID 13 kap 9) ê siōng-kē ê Current Ratio, siáⁿ chi̍t ê ū khà hó ê sán-phín hāu-lī?
Sím-mih kim-li̍t te̍k-sek tùi sia̍h-oa̍h ê kong-si ū kòan-hē, ài liáu-kái?
answer: Àng-chiáⁿ-ê sia̍h-oa̍h ê kong-si, siông-siông chhı̄-hián khah koân ê hiān-kim pí-lē kah bô-chè-chè pí-lē, chıl-chı̄ chin-chió ê chiap-siu kah té-kî kim-li̍t ê kiâⁿ-chhéng.
